xmlToHLVLParser

Class XmlReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • xmlToHLVLParser.XmlReader

  • public class XmlReader
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a class which is responsible for reading a XML file, loading that file into tree structure. and extract information from XML tree to create XML element object or XML dependency objects too.
    Version:
    1.5, 19/01/2019
    Author:
